subSubSection.paragraph:
Collophore. Anterior side with 16 chaetae, 10 spine-like chaetae, 1 proximal ciliated chaeta, 3 ciliated chaetae apically acuminate and 2 mac distally; posterior side with 10 ciliated chaetae (2 unpaired), 9 thin widely distributed and 1 thicker distally; lateral flap with about 29 chaetae, 4 smooth and 25 ciliated (
Fig. 29A
).
